默瑞看过雷米斯改写的剧本后决定加入，但两人很快就对电影基调产生分歧。默瑞觉得应该重点关注哲学内容，雷米斯认为喜剧元素才是重心<ref name="DOGRubin" /><ref name="new yorker" /><ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|16–17}}。制片商认可雷米斯的改写，觉得观众会更满意<ref name="DOGRubin" />。哥伦比亚影业回聘鲁宾，请他为剧本添加注解。鲁宾回归后写下许多注释，有些长达数页，内容实事求是的同时又不乏讽刺。默瑞对此颇感钦佩，建议聘请鲁宾直接参与剧本修改。<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|22}}

哥伦比亚影业要求增加解释男主角为什么身陷时间循环的内容<ref name="telegraph interview" />，坚持剧本说明原因后再开[[綠燈_(電影製作)|绿灯]]<ref name="TheWrapGypsy" />。据制片人特雷弗·阿尔伯特（{{lang|en|Trevor Albert}}）透露，公司高管曾询问：“为什么这天会不断重复……我很喜欢……但就是不明白为什么他会困在时间循环里”<ref name="TheWrapGypsy" />。鲁宾对此提供多种设想，如分手后怀恨在心的情人诅咒菲尔，或是疯狂科学的发明出现故障<ref name="TheWrapGypsy" />。阿尔伯特、雷米斯和鲁宾合作说服高管，三人一致同意这时再加戏会影响拍摄周期，如果非拍不可就直接在后期剪掉<ref name="TheWrapGypsy" />。

雷米斯与默瑞冲突不断，导演派鲁宾去和默瑞讨论剧本事宜，希望此举能让默瑞别再老是凌晨或一大清早地来电话。雷米斯致电鲁宾了解进展时，默瑞就要求鲁宾假装他不在旁边。<ref name="DOGRubin" /><ref name="new yorker" />鲁宾和默瑞曾前往庞克瑟托尼参观1992年土拨鼠日，充分了解节庆活动，但没有透露此行目的<ref>{{cite news | first = Jason | last = Nark | url = https://www.inquirer.com/news/groundhog-billmuray-punxsutawney-pittsburgh-holiday-weird-eagles-20190202.html | title = Groundhog Day, the improbable holiday that brings a shot in the arm to a former coal town | date = 2019-02-02 | access-date = 2021-01-18 | newspaper = [[費城詢問報|The Philadelphia Inquirer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107223942/https://www.inquirer.com/news/groundhog-billmuray-punxsutawney-pittsburgh-holiday-weird-eagles-20190202.html | archive-date = 2020-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="morning call">{{Cite news | url = https://www.mcall.com/news/mc-xpm-1993-02-12-2902959-story.html | title = Groundhog Sinks Teeth Into Film Role Bill Murray Calls Co-star 'Cranky' | first = Paul | last = Willistein | date = 1993-02-12 | access-date = 2021-01-18 | newspaper = The Morning Call | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150210051200/http://articles.mcall.com/1993-02-12/features/2902959_1_groundhog-day-punxsutawney-phil-harold-ramis | archive-date = 2015-02-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他们在[[纽约|纽约]]持续合作数月修改剧本<ref name="VultureRubin" /><ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|22–23}}，鲁宾觉得默瑞的创作风格趋于随意，对此颇感郁闷<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|23}}。电影开拍一个月前两人还在修改剧本，最终成品朝鲁宾的第二稿靠拢<ref name="DOGRubin" />。

接下来鲁宾又与雷米斯继续修改，两人负责不同部分，然后编辑对方改写的段落，雷米斯最后再用几天完善<ref name="DOGRubin" /><ref name="telegraph interview" />。鲁宾建议剧本不要保留任何时间印迹，令情节显得可能发生在任何时代<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|23}}<ref name="TheGuardianDirectors">{{cite news | first = Ryan | last = Gilbey | title = Groundhog Day: the perfect comedy, for ever | archive-date = 2021-01-15 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/feb/07/groundhog-day-perfect-comedy-for-ever | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115120051/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/feb/07/groundhog-day-perfect-comedy-for-ever | date = 2013-02-07 | newspaper = [[衛報|The Guardian]] | access-date = 2021-01-18 }}</ref>。鲁宾声称电影最终和他的剧本版本基本相符<ref name="LATIMesRamis" />，但对取消14岁男孩的桥段颇感遗憾，男孩在菲尔变得乐于助人时出场，行事像片头的菲尔般自命不凡、愤世嫉俗，两者对比鲜明<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|73}}。部分剧本情节没有在片中保留，如菲尔赌博、在教堂祈祷，以及脱光衣服吓得老人离开泳池的桥段，其中最后一个是经默瑞要求删除<ref name="DOGRubin" /><ref name="LATIMesRamis" />。此外，电影拍摄期间剧本仍时有修改<ref name="SeattleTimes">{{cite news | first = Moira | last = MacDonald | title = Actor Stephen Tobolowsky recalls how 'Groundhog Day' went from good to great | access-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180222003732/https://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/movies/actor-stephen-tobolowsky-recalls-how-lsquogroundhog-dayrsquo-went-from-good-to-great/ | archive-date = 2018-02-22 | url = https://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/movies/actor-stephen-tobolowsky-recalls-how-lsquogroundhog-dayrsquo-went-from-good-to-great/ | newspaper = [[西雅图时报|The Seattle Times]] | date = 2013-02-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="NorthWestHerald">{{cite news | first = Lindsay | last = Weber | title = Actor Stephen Tobolowsky discusses Woodstock, 'Groundhog Day' | url = https://www.shawlocal.com/2019/01/28/actor-stephen-tobolowsky-discusses-woodstock-groundhog-day/a3tssik/ | newspaper = Northwest Herald | date = 2019-01-30 | access-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001214215/https://www.nwherald.com/2019/01/28/actor-stephen-tobolowsky-discusses-woodstock-groundhog-day/a3tssik/ | archive-date = 2020-10-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 选角 ===
[[File:Chris_Elliott_by_Gage_Skidmore_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]

剧组曾考虑邀请[[切維·切斯|切維·切斯]]、[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]或[[米高·基頓|米高·基頓]]出演菲尔·康纳斯<ref>{{cite web | last = Fleming | first = Mike | title = Blast From The Past On ''Back To The Future'': How Frank Price Rescued Robert Zemeckis' Classic From Obscurity | url = https://deadline.com/2015/10/back-to-the-future-frank-price-rescued-robert-zemeckis-classic-1201590119/ | website = [[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] | access-date = 2020-12-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201220202705/https://deadline.com/2015/10/back-to-the-future-frank-price-rescued-robert-zemeckis-classic-1201590119/ | archive-date = 2020-12-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Hollywoodreporterhanks">{{cite journal | title = Happy 'Groundhog Day': Here's 5 Things You Didn't Know About the Movie | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/happy-groundhog-day-heres-5-769137 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date = 2015-02-02 | author = THR Staff | access-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201121111658/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/happy-groundhog-day-heres-5-769137 | archive-date = 2020-11-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="BusiInsideKeaton">{{cite journal | last = Acuna | first = Kristen | title = Why Michael Keaton Turned Down The Chance To Star In 'Groundhog Day' And 'Lost' | url = https://www.businessinsider.com/michael-keaton-turned-down-caddyshack-lost-2014-10 | journal = [[商业内幕|Business Insider]] | date = 2014-10-14 | access-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-date = 2020-05-07 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200507203849/https://www.businessinsider.com/michael-keaton-turned-down-caddyshack-lost-2014-10?r=US&IR=T }}</ref>。汉克斯是雷米斯的第一人选，但他谢绝邀约，不希望银幕形象局限为最后肯定会时来运转的好好先生。默瑞“无论戏里戏外都是霉运十足的混蛋”，由他出演观众就没那么容易预料情节发展。基顿自认以往扮演的人物都像菲尔一样扭曲、喜欢讽刺他人而且油嘴滑舌，不过他自承不理解剧情，事后表示后悔拒演本片。<ref name="Hollywoodreporterhanks" /><ref name="BusiInsideKeaton" />剧本中的菲尔更加年轻，后来剧组认为几乎所有成功的喜剧演员年纪都比较大，所以把人物写得更老<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|15}}。

默瑞和雷米斯是多年老友，自1974年起已在包括五部电影在内的各种项目合作，合作影片包括《[[肉丸_(电影)|肉丸]]》（''{{lang|en|Meatballs}}''）、《疯狂高尔夫》和《[[魔鬼剋星|魔鬼剋星]]》<ref name="new yorker" /><ref name="uproxx rift" />。鲁宾的设想是正常人身陷异常处境，所以笔下人物不致特别令人反感。默瑞演绎的菲尔更加愤世嫉俗，言辞冷嘲热讽、自命不凡，但还不至太过恶毒引起观众厌憎。<ref name="TheWrap" />鲁宾觉得默瑞表演功底达不到要求，期望[[奇雲·格連|奇雲·格連]]出演男主角<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|26}}。对此雷米斯表示：“别担心，比尔·默瑞就有这本事，他就是能让人又爱又恨”。麦克道威尔也有类似看法，称“他就是能让你开怀大笑的混球”。<ref name="TheWrap">{{cite web | first = Brian | last = Welk | title = Andie MacDowell on 'Groundhog Day' at 25: Bill Murray 'Asked Me to Really Slap Him' | url = https://www.thewrap.com/andie-macdowell-bill-murray-groundhog-day-25/ | date = 2018-02-12 | website = TheWrap | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125031510/https://www.thewrap.com/andie-macdowell-bill-murray-groundhog-day-25/ | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

剧组原计划请笑匠扮演丽塔，但主持试镜的阿尔伯特觉得没必要非请喜剧演员，真找来与默瑞不相上下的女笑匠反而对本片不利。丽塔无需像菲尔般妙语如珠，负责为电影提供人情温暖和智慧的一面。剧组认为麦克道威尔轻松自如的优雅气质与角色相符，演出期间她努力适应默瑞自然而然的即兴表演。在她看来，丽塔的幽默源自真诚，而且不致显得怪异。<ref name="TheWrap" />剧组还曾考虑邀请歌手[[多莉·艾莫絲|多莉·艾莫絲]]饰演丽塔<ref name="IndieWire">{{cite web | first = Oliver | last = Lyttleton | url = https://www.indiewire.com/2013/02/5-things-you-might-not-know-about-groundhog-day-on-its-20th-anniversary-101517/ | title = 5 Things You Might Not Know About 'Groundhog Day' On Its 20th Anniversary | date = 2013-02-12 | website = [[IndieWire|IndieWire]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019150632/https://www.indiewire.com/2013/02/5-things-you-might-not-know-about-groundhog-day-on-its-20th-anniversary-101517/ | archive-date = 2020-10-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

托布罗斯基试镜时的表演“极其令人反感”，因此获选出演本片<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|36}}。迈克尔·珊农扮演准新郎弗雷德，本片是他的电影处女作。他大部分出镜时间是餐馆桥段背景人物，剧组当时要求所有演员都在现场，不管镜头聚焦何处。<ref name="AVClubShannon">{{cite journal | first = Scott | last = Tobias | title = Michael Shannon | url = https://film.avclub.com/michael-shannon-1798218507 | date = 2009-10-12 | journal = The A.V. Club | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-10-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201002011214/https://film.avclub.com/michael-shannon-1798218507 }}</ref>演职人员找来活体土拨鼠斯库特“扮演”土拨鼠菲尔，庞克瑟托尼官员对电影不到该镇实地取景非常失望，拒绝剧组借用土拨鼠菲尔拍摄<ref name="Mentalfloss" /><ref name="PhillyBeast">{{cite news | first = Ryan | last = Murphy | title = Bill Murray And The Beast Filming "Groundhog Day" Turned Out To Be A Nightmare For The Actor. His Furry Co-star Had A Hankering For His Blood. | archive-date = 2016-08-19 | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2016-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160819161044/http://articles.philly.com/1993-02-07/entertainment/25955852_1_groundhog-s-day-phil-connors-punxsutawney-phil | newspaper = The Philadelphia Inquirer | date = 1993-02-07 | url = http://articles.philly.com/1993-02-07/entertainment/25955852_1_groundhog-s-day-phil-connors-punxsutawney-phil }}</ref>。斯库特是电影开拍数周前在伊利诺伊州附近荒野落入陷阱，不是专为电影拍摄饲养的土拨鼠<ref name="morning call" />。

=== 前期制作 ===
[[File:Gobblers_Knob_-_Punxsutawney,_Pennsylvania_(7086949891).jpg|thumb]]的火鸡丘（2012年）]]

剧组打算在“典型的美国小镇”实地取景，希望地点没有显著的时间或地域痕迹，确保绝大多数观众无法确定情节发生在何时何地<ref name="Varietyat25" />。从宾夕法尼亚电影委员会提供的庞克瑟托尼地点探查录像带来看，该镇缺乏剧本所需取景地，显然不适合实地拍摄<ref name="Varietyat25" /><ref name="morning call" />。庞克瑟托尼是缺乏必要设施的乡间小镇，距最近的大城市[[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]有130公里，甚至无法向演职人员提供充足的住宿条件<ref name="morning call" /><ref name="AboutPittsburgh">{{cite web | first = Albrecht | last = Powell | url = https://www.thoughtco.com/what-is-groundhog-day-2707298 | title = What the Heck is Groundhog Day Anyway? | website = [[Dotdash|Thoughtco.com]] | date = 2020-01-08 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015850/https://www.thoughtco.com/what-is-groundhog-day-2707298 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

雷米斯是芝加哥人，很高兴电影到伊利诺伊州取景，知道哪些地方能满足拍摄需求<ref name="Varietyat25" /><ref name="morning call" />。取景地要通公路，不能离大都市太远，而且冬天风景优美，能够满足尽快完成拍摄的其他需求，导演还希望当地要有类似庞克瑟托尼[[大街|正街]]的街道<ref name="morning call" /><ref name="AboutPittsburgh" />。负责地点探查的鲍勃·哈金斯（{{lang|en|Bob Hudgins}}）认为[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]][[愛阿華縣_(威斯康辛州)|爱荷华县]][[米纳勒尔波因特_(威斯康星州)|米纳勒尔波因特]]（{{lang|en|Mineral Point}}）能满足需求，剧组前往视察期间在该州[[索克縣_(威斯康辛州)|索克县]][[巴拉布_(威斯康星州)|巴拉布]]（{{lang|en|Baraboo}}）停留，感觉当地的[[城市廣場|城镇广场]]对拍摄助益很大，在此取景哪怕没有导演设想的街道也利大于弊。雷米斯于是要求取景地最好在芝加哥附近，也有类似广场。<ref name="WoodstockIndependent">{{cite news | first = Matt | last = Fagerholm | title = How Bob Hudgins saved 'Groundhog Day' | url = https://variety.com/2018/film/news/groundhog-day-at-25-bill-murray-1202691391/ | date = 2011-01-26 | newspaper = The Woodstock Independent | access-date = 2011-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713134414/http://www.thewoodstockindependent.com/story.php?id=786 | archive-date = 2011-07-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

剧组探查六十多个城镇后来到伊利诺伊州[[伍德斯托克_(伊利諾伊州)|伍德斯托克]]，哈金斯为1987年喜剧片《[[落难见真情|落难见真情]]》（''{{lang|en|Planes, Trains and Automobiles}}''）选址期间来过此地。伍德斯托克约有2.5万居民，相对偏远，没有明显时代痕迹。雷米斯和阿尔伯特经哈金斯安排在伍德斯托克歌剧院钟楼上眺望，随后决定就在该镇取景。<ref name="morning call" /><ref name="WoodstockIndependent" />片中致使菲尔摔倒的路陷也是在伍德斯托克所挖<ref name="Varietyat25" /><ref name="WoodstockIndependent" />。

选址人员觉得伊利诺伊州[[麥克亨利_(伊利諾伊州)|麦克亨利]]镇外的森林保护区可以用来拍摄火鸡丘（{{lang|en|Gobbler's Knob}}）桥段，但剧组后来决定就在城镇广场搭建外景<ref name="WoodstockIndependent" />，利用详细的介绍和视频制作比例模型<ref name="Varietyat25" /><ref name="morning call" /><ref name="AboutPittsburgh" />，对小镇的影响大幅提升。各拍摄现场共计动用成千上万的群众演员，当地企业联手施压，担心电影拍摄花费时间太长，对城镇广场和店面影响太大。据哈金斯透落，起初联手的企业有23家，但经他努力降至14家，对此他颇为自傲。镇议会无法对是否同意电影继续拍摄达成一致。<ref name="WoodstockIndependent" />影片摄制收尾后，三家企业业主起诉哥伦比亚影业，要求补偿这段时间的营收损失。其中一起案件庭外合解，另外两起结果不明。<ref name="ChicagoTribunePremiere">{{Cite news | first = Phil | last = Borchmann | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1993-02-05-9303175765-story.html | title = Fur's No Longer Flying Now That 'Groundhog Day' Is Here | date = 1993-02-05 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200426202225/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1993-02-05-9303175765-story.html | archive-date = 2020-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 摄制 ===
[[File:Groundhog_day_tip_top_bistro.jpg|thumb]]

电影1992年3月16日开始[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]，持续86天后在6月10日结束<ref>{{cite news | title = Groundhog Day | url = http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/21023/Groundhog-Day/misc-notes.html | publisher = [[特纳经典电影频道|Turner Classic Movies]] | access-date = 2020-04-25 | archive-date = 2020-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200425060901/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/21023/Groundhog-Day/misc-notes.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。摄制预算估计在1460至3000万美元<ref name="VarietyBudget" /><ref name="morning call" /><ref name="TheNumbers">{{Cite web | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Groundhog-Day#tab=summary | title = Groundhog Day – Box Office Data, DVD and Blu-ray Sales, Movie News, Cast and Crew Information | website = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727053752/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Groundhog-Day#tab=summary | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，取景地以伍德斯托克为主，其他地点包括伊利诺伊州[[卡里_(伊利諾伊州)|卡里]]和加利福尼亚州好莱坞<ref name="morning call" /><ref name="PennLive">{{cite news | first = Lisa | last = Wardle | title = 2 Punxsutawneys: Compare 'Groundhog Day' film locations to the real town | url = https://www.pennlive.com/life/2017/01/groundhog_day_filming_locations.html | newspaper = The Patriot-News | date = 2019-05-22 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200812205958/https://www.pennlive.com/life/2017/01/groundhog_day_filming_locations.html | archive-date = 2020-08-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

电影拍摄期间天气变化很大，大部分镜头是在滴水成冰的条件下摄制<ref name="Varietyat25" />。默瑞估计气温通常在零下7°C范围，严寒一直持续到五月底。默瑞还称，每天户外工作长达12小时，导致皮肤生涩，人也非常烦躁。<ref name="morning call" />拍摄工作在夏初接近尾声，剧组用假雪拍摄外景，演员不得不在日益炎热的气温条件下一直穿着冬装<ref name="AVClubShannon" />。雷米斯尚未决定菲尔遇见内德时天气如何，于是在不同天气条件下各拍至少一遍，最后选定阴天，代表时间循环即将结束<ref name="Varietyat25" />。片中的撞车戏共花费两周拍摄，对此天气影响很大<ref name="JournalStandard">{{Cite news | first = Adam | last = Poulisse | date = 2008-02-02 | url = https://www.journalstandard.com/news/20180202/william-charles-construction-employees-recall-groundhog-day-scenes-filmed-at-workplace-as-movie-turns-25 | title = William Charles Construction employees recall 'Groundhog Day' scenes filmed at workplace as movie turns 25 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | newspaper = The Journal Standard | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200426200627/https://www.journalstandard.com/news/20180202/william-charles-construction-employees-recall-groundhog-day-scenes-filmed-at-workplace-as-movie-turns-25 | archive-date = 2020-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

雷米斯和默瑞冲突不断，为电影摄制蒙上阴影，雷米斯的着眼点是浪漫喜剧，但默瑞期望影片更具内涵<ref name="Varietyat25" /><ref name="ReadersDigest">{{cite journal | first = Kelly | last = Bryant | title = Why Bill Murray Hated the Movie "Groundhog Day" | url = https://www.rd.com/article/why-bill-murray-hated-groundhog-day/ | journal = [[读者文摘|Reader's Digest]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200815210020/https://www.rd.com/article/why-bill-murray-hated-groundhog-day/ | archive-date = 2020-08-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。默瑞此时正与玛格丽特·凯利（{{lang|en|Margaret Kelly}}）离婚，两人育有两个孩子<ref name="LATIMesRamis" />，本片拍摄期间他一直很痛苦，行为失常、乱发脾气，而且经常抵触导演决定<ref name="uproxx rift" /><ref name="ReadersDigest" />。据雷米斯回忆，默瑞多次迟到，行为举止缺乏理智乃至不可理喻<ref name="ReadersDigest" />。两人对剧本及其他演员的表现也有分歧<ref name="LATIMesRamis" />。据珊农回忆，某次他不知何故得罪默瑞，雷米斯听闻后要求默瑞公开向珊农道歉<ref name="AVClubShannon" />。托布罗斯基声称，默瑞在开拍前到面包店买下所有糕点扔向围观群众，还要求托布罗斯基在旁帮他拿糕点<ref name="NorthWestHerald" />。
[[File:Wdstckoperahouse1.JPG|thumb]]

剧本在拍摄期间继续修改。托布罗斯基首次出场前拿到新剧本，他估计有三分之一与之前看到的版本不同。例如菲尔首次发现循环后折断铅笔验证，后来又上旅馆房间墙上喷添，毁坏房内物品，把头发剪成[[莫霍克发型|莫霍克发型]]；这组镜头共花费三天拍完而且耗资不菲，但雷米斯决定删除，换成更加平和、简单，不那么神经质的情节。菲尔在修改后的剧本中更加倒霉。反复自杀的情节本来时间更早，但经修改后移，以增加第三幕篇幅，展示他改头换面，拥抱生活。<ref name="SeattleTimes" /><ref name="NorthWestHerald" />

默里为拍部分镜头情愿冒受伤的风险。为拍摄菲尔步入大水坑的镜头，他用保鲜膜、氯丁橡胶和两双袜子包住脚。镜头拍好后，他咆哮着冲进服装部用吹风机把脚吹干，以免冻伤。<ref name="Varietyat25" />默瑞要求麦克道威尔在拍戏时真的扇他耳光；拍摄菲尔和儿童打雪仗时，导演指示小演员用力扔雪球<ref name="TheWrap" /><ref name="ReadersDigest" />。拍摄菲尔开车带着土拨鼠冲下悬崖的镜头时，土拨鼠斯库特咬伤演员指关节，默瑞戴着手套，但还是被小家伙咬破皮，后来镜头重拍时，斯库特又咬他一口<ref name="PhillyBeast" /><ref name="Mentalfloss" />。

片尾菲尔醒来看到身边的丽塔，表明他至此脱离循环，默瑞觉得男主角此时所穿的衣服可能影响观众理解。雷米斯为此征求演职人员意见，结果分成两派，一方认为应该是前一晚所穿的衣服，另一方认为应该是不同的衣服，表明两人发生亲密关系。<ref name="Varietyat25" />双方人数不相上下，最后剧组中的青年女子打破僵局，相同衣服派胜出，因为“别的不管穿什么……都会沦为败笔”<ref name="Varietyat25" />。片尾菲尔和丽塔走出旅馆，默瑞把剧本台词“咱们在这儿住吧”即兴发挥成“咱们租个房吧”<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|80–81}}。

电影在伍德斯托克及周边许多地点制作，伍德斯托克城镇广场多次出镜，非常显著。前法院大楼酒吧充当片中丽塔下塌旅店的酒吧。伍德斯托克歌剧院是丽塔所住旅馆和菲尔跳楼自杀的外景地。<ref name="PennLive" /><ref name="LocationHub">{{Cite web | url = https://www.locationshub.com/blog/2013/10/26/about-those-famous-groundhog-days-filming-locations | title = About Those Famous Groundhog's Day Filming Locations | date = 2011-02-02 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | website = Location Hub | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190424001451/https://www.locationshub.com/blog/2013/10/26/about-those-famous-groundhog-days-filming-locations | archive-date = 2019-04-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。樱桃街旅馆是在民宅取外景，内景另行搭建<ref name="PennLive" />。伍德斯托克城市保龄球馆用于拍摄片中保龄球馆桥段<ref name="LocationHub" />。菲尔和丽塔见面的尖顶咖啡厅是专为本片搭建，剧组离开后，当地市场需求促使咖啡厅继续经营<ref name="LocationHub" /><ref>{{Cite news | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|HuffPost]] | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/celebrate-groundhog-day-o_b_6573676 | title = Celebrate Groundhog Day Over and Over Again With This Filming Locations Guide | date = 2015-01-30 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200426185825/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/celebrate-groundhog-day-o_b_6573676 | archive-date = 2020-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。单身汉拍卖活动是在伍德斯托克驼鹿旅馆拍摄<ref name="PennLive" /><ref name="LocationHub" />。菲尔开车冲下悬崖是在距伍德斯托克约55公里的伊利诺伊州[[拉夫斯帕克_(伊利諾伊州)|拉夫斯帕克]]尼姆兹采石场取景，剧组用轨道把两辆车推入采石场供导演选择，再用烟火技术炸掉汽车<ref name="JournalStandard" />。

