1993年，适合合家观赏的电影非常繁荣<ref name="LAtimesYear1993">{{cite news | first = David J. | last = Fox | title = The Year In Movies : '93 A Record-smasher At The Box Office : 'Mrs. Doubtfire,' 'Pelican Brief' Propel Final Week And 'Jurassic Park' Chews Up The Competition As Industry Receipts Hit $5.2 Billion. | date = 1993-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009083408/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1994-01-03-ca-8097-story.html | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1994-01-03-ca-8097-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这一来是因为外界批评好莱坞电影充斥暴力色情，另一方面也是经济衰退时期娱乐观众所需<ref name="LATimesFamily">{{cite news | first = Elaine | last = Dutka | title = A Startling New Concept: Family Films : With money tight and criticism of sex and violence high, studios are looking closer at PG's power | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009160629/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-22-ca-13950-story.html | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-22-ca-13950-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-03-22 | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="NYTFAmily">{{cite news | first = Bernard | last = Weinraub | title = Hollywood Is Testing Family Values' Value | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1993/12/16/movies/new-york-critics-honor-schindler-s-list.html | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1992-11-12 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-11-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201123122652/https://www.nytimes.com/1993/12/16/movies/new-york-critics-honor-schindler-s-list.html }}</ref>。电影拍摄成本越来越高，合家欣赏的电影无论院线发行还是家用媒体租售都更有希望获利。截至1993年，北美洲票房最高的三部家庭导向电影分别是《[[E.T.外星人|E.T.外星人]]》、《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星球大战]]》和《[[小鬼當家|小鬼當家]]》。这类电影往往能吸引回头客，还能提供更丰富的周边商品机遇。<ref name="LATimesFamily" /><ref name="NYTFAmily" />时任哥伦比亚影业总裁马克·坎顿（{{lang|en|Mark Canton}}）表示，与成人导向电影相比，评为[[美国电影分级制度|PG级]]的作品票房破亿希望大增。《土拨鼠之日》就是PG级，不限制观众年龄，评论认为本片有望闷声发大财。<ref>{{cite journal | first = Peter | last = Bart | title = Lowest common denominator doesn't work anymore | url = https://variety.com/1993/voices/columns/lowest-common-denominator-doesn-t-work-anymore-1117859410/ | date = 1993-03-21 | journal = Variety | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008193758/https://variety.com/1993/voices/columns/lowest-common-denominator-doesn-t-work-anymore-1117859410/ | archive-date = 2020-10-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | first = John Evan | last = Frook | title = B.O. year: First among sequels | url = https://variety.com/1993/film/news/b-o-year-first-among-sequels-102668/ | date = 1993-01-05 | journal = Variety | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009124316/https://variety.com/1993/film/news/b-o-year-first-among-sequels-102668/ | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

1993年上映的家庭导向电影众多，除《土拨鼠之日》外还有《[[人鱼童话|人鱼童话]]》（''{{lang|en|Free Willy}}''）、《[[幻影英雄|幻影英雄]]》（''{{lang|en|Last Action Hero}}''），以及万众嘱目、上映后打破历史电影票房纪录的《[[侏羅紀公園|侏羅紀公園]]》<ref>{{cite news | first = Craig | last = Hlavaty | title = 1993: The Greatest Year for Movies in the History of Movies Ever? | url = https://www.houstonpress.com/arts/1993-the-greatest-year-for-movies-in-the-history-of-movies-ever-6398091 | date = 2013-03-28 | newspaper = Houston Press | access-date = 2020-10-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001203135/https://www.houstonpress.com/arts/1993-the-greatest-year-for-movies-in-the-history-of-movies-ever-6398091 | archive-date = 2020-10-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年发行的各类电影佳作众多，堪称百花齐放，史上少有<ref>{{cite news | first = Chris | last = Hicks | title = The Best & The Worst Of 1993 | url = https://www.deseret.com/1993/12/24/19083339/the-best-the-worst-of-1993 | date = 1993-12-24 | newspaper = Deseret News | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-04-26 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://archive.today/20200426223931/https://www.deseret.com/1993/12/24/19083339/the-best-the-worst-of-1993 }}</ref><ref name="RogerEbert1993">{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | author-link = 罗杰·伊伯特 | title = The Best 10 Movies of 1993 | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/roger-ebert/the-best-10-movies-of-1993 | date = 1993-12-31 | website = RogerEbert.com | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-11-13 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201113211249/https://www.rogerebert.com/roger-ebert/the-best-10-movies-of-1993 }}</ref>，既有《[[窈窕奶爸|窈窕奶爸]]》、《[[不道德的交易|不道德的交易]]》这类票房大片，又有《[[辛德勒的名单|辛德勒的名单]]》、《[[费城故事_(1993年电影)|费城]]》等广受好评的杰作<ref name="TheNumbers1993">{{Cite web | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1993 | title = Top 1993 Movies at the Domestic Box Office | website = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008224131/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1993 | archive-date = 2020-10-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="RogerEbert1993" /><ref name="Collider1993">{{cite web | first = Matt | last = Goldberg | title = The Year in Film: 1993 | url = https://collider.com/1993-movies/#film-history | date = 2018-03-19 | website = [[Collider|Collider]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200105122406/https://collider.com/1993-movies/#film-history | archive-date = 2020-01-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，还有此时不受重视，但日后终成经典的《[[年少轻狂_(1993年电影)|年少轻狂]]》（''{{lang|en|Dazed and Confused}}''）、《[[蝙蝠侠：幽灵的面具|蝙蝠侠大战幻影人]]》和《[[怪誕城之夜_(電影)|圣诞夜惊魂]]》<ref name="Collider1993" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Emma | last = Pearse | title = Remember 1993? When the Best Movies Came Out? | url = https://www.tribecafilm.com/news/the-best-movies-of-1993-to-do-list | date = 2013-07-25 | website = [[翠貝卡電影節|Tribeca Film]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111232435/https://tribecafilm.com/news/the-best-movies-of-1993-to-do-list | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Arielle | last = Duhaime-Ross | title = The greatest film debate of our generation: 1993 or 1994? | url = https://www.theverge.com/2014/8/22/6056729/1993-vs-1994-what-was-the-best-year-in-film#1993 | date = 2014-08-22 | website = [[The_Verge|The Verge]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111220711/https://www.theverge.com/2014/8/22/6056729/1993-vs-1994-what-was-the-best-year-in-film#1993 | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

1993年2月4日，《土拨鼠之日》在洛杉矶[[西木區|西木區]][[福克斯剧院_(洛杉矶西木区)|福克斯剧院]]首映。首映式预算有限，默瑞没有参与，出席嘉宾包括笑匠[[鲁德尼·丹泽菲尔德|鲁德尼·丹泽菲尔德]]（{{lang|en|Rodney Dangerfield}}）、女演员[[凯瑟琳·奥哈拉|凯瑟琳·奥哈拉]]、[[米密·罗杰斯|米密·罗杰斯]]（{{lang|en|Mimi Rogers}}）和[[维吉妮娅·马德森|维吉妮娅·马德森]]。门票销售收入四万美元，事后捐给硬皮病研究基金会与转折点庇护所。<ref>{{cite news | first = Bill | last = Higgins | title = The Less-Than-Lavish Premiere | date = 1993-02-08 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008151422/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-08-vw-1066-story.html | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-08-vw-1066-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | archive-date = 2020-10-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>次日电影又在伊利诺伊州[[克里斯托爾湖_(伊利諾伊州)|克里斯托爾湖]]第二次首映，随后拍卖片中使用的道具和签名装备，所有收益捐赠伍德斯托克学区<ref name="ChicagoTribunePremiere" />。

电影在法国和巴西上映时分别更名《无尽之日》（{{lang|en|''A Day Without End''}}）和《爱的黑洞》（{{lang|en|''The Black Hole of Love''}}）<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|8}}。

=== 票房 ===
1993年2月12日，本片在北美洲1640家剧院全面上映，当天收入1250万美元，平均每家7632美元。这周适逢[[华盛顿生日|华盛顿生日]]，周末假期有四天，票房升至1460万美元，平均每家电影院8934美元。开局表现在历年冬季上映的电影中仅次于《[[反斗智多星|反-{斗}-智多星]]》（''{{lang|en|Wayne's World}}''，1800万美元，1992年）。《土拨鼠之日》上映首周登顶票房排行榜，超过上映第二周的浪漫剧情片《[[似是故人来_(电影)|似是故人来]]》（''{{lang|en|Sommersby}}''，990万美元）和历险喜剧片《[[看狗在说话|看狗在说话]]》（''{{lang|en|Homeward Bound: The Incredible Journey}}''，810万美元）<ref name="BOMWeekendBrkDwn">{{cite web | title = Groundhog Day – Domestic Weekend | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2723644929/weekend/?ref_=bo_rl_tab#tabs | website = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008195216/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2723644929/weekend/?ref_=bo_rl_tab#tabs | archive-date = 2020-10-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = David J. | last = Fox | title = Presidents' Day Weekend Box Office : 'Groundhog' Has Its Day | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-17-ca-187-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-02-17 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009013442/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-17-ca-187-story.html | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first = Beth | last = Kleid | title = Movies | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-15-ca-74-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-02-17 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201010092706/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-15-ca-74-story.html | archive-date = 2020-10-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。电影放映胶片约售出八成，观众意向调查显示六成五的观众表示“绝对推荐”<ref>{{cite journal | first = Richard | last = Natale | title = 'Weapon's' loaded at nat'l B.O. | url = https://variety.com/1993/film/news/weapon-s-loaded-at-nat-l-b-o-103757/ | date = 1993-02-07 | journal = Variety | access-date = 2020-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201010164219/https://variety.com/1993/film/news/weapon-s-loaded-at-nat-l-b-o-103757/ | archive-date = 2020-10-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影片上映第二周收入930万美元成功卫冕<ref>{{cite news | title = Weekend Box Office | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-23-ca-341-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-02-23 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201012171602/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-02-23-ca-341-story.html | archive-date = 2020-10-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，第三周拿下760万美元，被新上映的《[[怒火风暴|城市英雄]]》以870万美元挤到第二<ref name="BOMWeekendBrkDwn" /><ref>{{cite news | first = David J. | last = Fox | title = Weekend Box Office : People Like Him in Ruthless Roles | archive-date = 2020-10-12 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-02-ca-50-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-03-02 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201012210210/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-02-ca-50-story.html }}</ref>。接下来《土拨鼠之日》还在票房榜前十停留四周，七周合计5760万美元。此后影片基本是在前十以外徘徊，仅四月中旬复活节周末一度冲到第二，第15周开始在低价影院上映后再升至第七。<ref name="BOMWeekendBrkDwn" /><ref>{{cite news | first = David J. | last = Fox | title = Weekend Box Office : 'Sliver' Takes Big Slice Out of Market | archive-date = 2020-10-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201012123041/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-05-25-ca-39560-story.html | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-05-25-ca-39560-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-05-25 | access-date = 2021-01-19 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Groundhog-Day#tab=box-office | title = Groundhog Day (1993) | website = The Numbers | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200727053752/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Groundhog-Day#tab=box-office | archive-date = 2020-07-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

《土拨鼠之日》票房总额约7090万美元<ref name="TheNumbers" />，虽未打破任何纪录，但仍算得上商业成功的作品<ref name="TheGuardianDirectors" /><ref>{{cite news | first = Jane | last = Galbraith | title = A look inside Hollywood and the movies. : HOPE AND 'GLORY' : Funny How a Groundhog Can Generate Buzz | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-07-ca-7952-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-03-07 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201015220142/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-03-07-ca-7952-story.html | archive-date = 2020-10-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="PasteHit">{{cite journal | first = Jim | last = Vorel | url = https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/groundhog-day/groundhog-day-best-quarantine-movies/ | title = Why Bill Murray's Groundhog Day Is the Ultimate Quarantine Movie | date = 2020-03-30 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | journal = Paste | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201119004528/https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/groundhog-day/groundhog-day-best-quarantine-movies/ | archive-date = 2020-11-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。本片在1993年电影票房排行榜名列第十，第九和第八分别是《人鱼童话》（7800万美元）和《[[巔峰戰士|绝岭雄风]]》（8400万美元）<ref name="LAtimesYear1993" />。如果只计算1993年末上映、大部分票房是在1994年达成的电影，《土拨鼠之日》收入排名第14<ref name="TheNumbers1993" />。本片在北美洲以外国家和地区的票房收入缺乏记载<ref name="TheNumbers" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Groundhog Day | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2723644929/ | website = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127012153/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2723644929/ | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1997年，业界专家估算制片商因本片共计收入（即减去院线发行分成）3250万美元<ref>{{cite journal | title = Rental champs: Rate of return | url = https://variety.com/1997/digital/features/rental-champs-rate-of-return-1116680329/ | date = 1997-12-15 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210108132440/https://variety.com/1997/digital/features/rental-champs-rate-of-return-1116680329/ | archive-date = 2021-01-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
=== 专业评论 ===
[[File:Stephen_tobolowsky_2012.jpg|thumb]]

《土拨鼠之日》获评论界普遍好评<ref>{{cite journal | title = Readers' Poll: The 20 Greatest Bill Murray Movies | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-lists/readers-poll-the-20-greatest-bill-murray-movies-14966/1-groundhog-day-42284/ | date = 2014-03-18 | journal = [[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002849/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-lists/readers-poll-the-20-greatest-bill-murray-movies-14966/1-groundhog-day-42284/ | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[影院评分|影院评分]]调查表明影迷的平均评级为“{{lang|en|B}}+”（最高“{{lang|en|A}}+”，最低“{{lang|en|F}}”）<ref>需在“{{lang|en|FIND CINEMASCORE}}”下面的搜索框输入电影原名“{{lang|en|Groundhog Day}}”，页面会自动显示评分：{{cite web | url = https://www.cinemascore.com | title = Cinemascore | website = [[影院评分|CinemaScore]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2018-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180102130540/https://www.cinemascore.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

本片与默瑞和雷米斯过去合作的作品相比变化很大<ref name="LATimesReview">{{cite news | first = Kenneth | last = Turan | title = From the Archives: Bill Murray's 'Groundhog Day': It's deja vu all over again | url = https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-bill-murray-groundhog-day-review-20160202-story.html | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1993-02-12 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210106142523/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-bill-murray-groundhog-day-review-20160202-story.html | archive-date = 2021-01-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[肯尼斯·图兰|肯尼斯·图兰]]（{{lang|en|Kenneth Turan}}）认可电影从小处着眼，情感温和亲切<ref name="LATimesReview" />。哈尔·欣森（{{lang|en|Hal Hinson}}）声称本片是1982年《[[杜絲先生|窈窕淑男]]》（同样有默瑞参演）过后最出色的美国喜剧片，证明雷米斯把握喜剧时机的能力，毫不掩饰做作地呈现巧妙剧情<ref name="WashingtonPostReview">{{cite web | first = Hal | last = Hinson | archive-date = 2020-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201016063234/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/groundhogdaypghinson_a0a7e9.htm | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | date = 1993-02-12 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/groundhogdaypghinson_a0a7e9.htm | title = Groundhog Day | access-date = 2021-01-19 }}</ref>。影评人认为《土拨鼠之日》就像《生活多美好》结合超现实科幻/恐怖电视剧《[[迷離境界|迷离时空]]》<ref name="NYTReview" /><ref name="WashingtonPostReview" /><ref name="THRReview">{{cite journal | first = Duane | last = Byrge | title = 'Groundhog Day': THR's 1993 Review | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/groundhog-day-thrs-1993-review-769136 | date = 1993-02-12 | journal = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201029154253/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/groundhog-day-thrs-1993-review-769136 | archive-date = 2020-10-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]将本片与同样由默瑞主演的圣诞喜剧《[[孤寒财主|孤寒财主]]》（''{{lang|en|Scrooged}}''）对比，两部电影剧情都有自私到无私的转变。伊伯特称，与严酷且牢骚满腹的《孤寒财主》相比，《土拨鼠之日》让人倍感乐观<ref name="EbertReviewOrig">{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | title = Groundhog Day | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/groundhog-day-1993 | date = 1993-02-12 | website = RogerEbert.com | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127233843/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/groundhog-day-1993 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影评人大多认为本片道德立场显著，但对立场呈现看法不一。[[德森·汤姆森|德森·汤姆森]]（{{lang|en|Desson Thomson}}）感觉影片起初引人入胜，可惜最后变质成好莱坞式道德童话<ref name="WashingtonPostRevHowe">{{cite news | first = Desson | last = Thomson | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/groundhogdaypghowe_a0af6c.htm | title = Groundhog Day | date = 1993-02-12 | access-date = 2021-01-19 | newspaper = The Washington Post | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200516055839/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/groundhogdaypghowe_a0af6c.htm | archive-date = 2020-05-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。图兰认为电影开头类似好莱坞传统题材，但真挚情感足以让观众坚持到底，“浪漫的纯真”令影片不致落入俗套公式<ref name="LATimesReview" />。欣森指出，剧情呈现的道德立场温和，不致污辱观众智商，也不强求认可。在他看来，菲尔为人虽有改善，但一直都很混蛋。<ref name="WashingtonPostReview" />[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）赞扬本片在多愁善感和虚无主义间保持平衡<ref name="NYTReview" />。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》发文称赞本片认可小镇道德理念，而且认同这些理念能从积极方向影响菲尔<ref name="THRReview" />。《[[新政治家|新政治家]]》的评论声称，影片融玩世不恭与乐观向上于一体<ref name="Gilbey-2004" />{{rp|11}}。

部分评论批评电影基调不一，节奏欠佳，而且部分桥段持续时间太长<ref name="VarietyReview" />。[[欧文·格里伯曼|欧文·格里伯曼]]（{{lang|en|Owen Glieberman}}）将《土拨鼠之日》与时间旅行电影《[[回到未来|回到未来]]》对比，感觉后者布局更巧妙。在他看来，本片部分镜头更像独立喜剧小品，而非大型作品相互配合的环节<ref name="EWReview">{{cite journal | date = 1993-02-12 | first = Owen | last = Gleiberman | title = Groundhog Day | url = https://ew.com/article/1993/02/12/groundhog-day-3/ | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925093639/https://ew.com/article/1993/02/12/groundhog-day-3/ | archive-date = 2020-09-25 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-01-19 }}</ref>。汤姆森觉得持续循环的情节对影片不利，让人感觉电影毫无进展<ref name="WashingtonPostRevHowe" />；但欣森看法截然相反，认为各个情节的微小变动足以保持观众兴趣，逐渐呈现“极富想象力”的复杂情节<ref name="WashingtonPostReview" />。评论感觉片中笑料趋于温和，观众往往轻声一笑而非捧腹不止<ref name="EWReview" /><ref name="NYTReview" />，不过欣森倒觉得“非常好笑”<ref name="WashingtonPostReview" />。《好莱坞报道》指出片中笑料和讽刺内容很多，但效果都因菲尔与丽塔的爱情故事减弱<ref name="THRReview" />。还有影评人称电影看似喜剧，背后内容其实深刻得多。伊伯特称赞本片在喜剧外表之下包含深切情感<ref name="EbertReviewOrig" />，马斯林自称对电影的第一印象颇为轻快，但后来却觉得“意外感人”<ref name="NYTReview" />。

默瑞的演出赢得一致赞誉<ref name="VarietyReview" /><ref name="LATimesReview" /><ref name="WashingtonPostReview" /><ref name="WashingtonPostRevHowe" />，影评人认为是他让菲尔的转变真实可信，对本片成功至关重要<ref name="VarietyReview" /><ref name="NYTReview" /><ref name="RevSiskel">{{cite news | first = Gene | last = Siskel | title = Bill Murray Bundles Up For 'Groundhog Day' Cosmic Chill | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1993-02-12-9303180540-story.html | date = 1993-02-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925093637/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1993-02-12-9303180540-story.html | archive-date = 2020-09-25 | dead-url = no | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | access-date = 2021-01-19 }}</ref>。[[吉恩·西斯克|吉恩·西斯克]]（{{lang|en|Gene Siskel}}）认为其他演员都会导致本片沦为“糖精”（指过于甜蜜的浪漫爱情）<ref name="RevSiskel" />。图兰指出，默瑞天生就让人感觉不好惹，而且喜剧形象往往浑身是刺，令剧情不致显得无病呻吟。他还将默瑞过去的粗暴演出拿来对比，觉得新形象更加亲切。<ref name="LATimesReview" />欣森声称默瑞的喜剧演出达到新高度，是他让电影更显情真意切、积极向上。欣森还特别称赞菲尔拥抱生活、热心助人后依然不时口吐讥诮的形象。<ref name="WashingtonPostReview" />格里伯曼认为，男主角的冷漠足以吸引观众注意。在他看来，默瑞不适合扮演回头浪子，但在片中表现足以让人信服<ref name="EWReview" />。伊伯特感觉时而冷嘲热讽的菲尔比“重新做人”后要好笑得多<ref name="EbertReviewOrig" />。

影评人认可麦克道威尔的表演，西斯克声称她每次出镜都让人眼前一亮<ref name="RevSiskel" />。马斯林称赞她的演出令人心旷神怡<ref name="NYTReview" />。欣森认为麦克道威尔是完美的喜剧演员，男女主角的银幕化学反应“超凡脱俗”<ref name="WashingtonPostReview" />。托布罗斯基诠释的保险销售员笑料十足、广受好评<ref name="VarietyReview" /><ref name="NYTReview" />。

