/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1993-12-09-ca-117-story.html | archive-date = 2020-04-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>但未获[[第66届奥斯卡金像奖|第66届奥斯卡金像奖]]提名<ref>{{cite web | title = The 66th Academy Awards 1994 | url = https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1994 | publisher = [[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | access-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201211221229/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1994 | archive-date = 2020-12-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

