ws | first = Stefanno | last = Rellandini | title = "Groundhog Day" coming to DVD, again | date = 2007-12-13 | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180614040125/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-groundhog/groundhog-day-coming-to-dvd-again-idUSN1365379420071213 | archive-date = 2018-06-14 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.reuters.com/article/us-groundhog/groundhog-day-coming-to-dvd-again-idUSN1365379420071213 }}</ref>，电影经过雷米斯监督的数码修复，除导演评论音轨和《时间的重量》外，还有土拨鼠主题纪录短片、删剪镜头和采访雷米斯的内容<ref name="HomeMediaForbes" /><ref name="HomeMediaEWDVD" /><ref>{{cite web | first = David | last = McCutcheon | title = Groundhog Day Again! | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/26/groundhog-day-again | date = 2007-11-26 | website = IGN | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200508112806/https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/26/groundhog-day-again | archive-date = 2020-05-08 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-01-20 }}</ref>。15周年版内容在2009年再发[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]，新增[[画中画|画中画]]功能，托布罗斯基扮成内德介绍电影和幕后故事<ref>{{cite web | first = R.L. | last = Shaffer | title = Groundhog Day Blu-ray Review | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/02/groundhog-day-blu-ray-review | date = 2009-02-02 | website = IGN | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190728233833/https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/02/groundhog-day-blu-ray-review | archive-date = 2019-07-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

