1993年电影发行后不久就有报导宣布本片确定不拍续集<ref name="Sequel" />。2004年的意大利电影《鹳日》（{{lang|it|''È già ieri''}}）是《土拨鼠之日》重拍片，鲁宾是该片故事创作人<ref name="VultureRubin" /><ref name="IndieWire" />。麦克道威尔在接受采访时表示，默瑞完全没有这方面意愿，所以本片不可能拍续集<ref>{{cite journal | first = Ciara | last = McVey | title = Andie MacDowell: Bill Murray "Never Going to Do" 'Groundhog Day' Reboot – In Studio | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031092212/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/andie-macdowell-bill-murray-never-going-do-groundhog-day-reboot-studio-1099307 | date = 2018-04-03 | journal = The Hollywood Reporter | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/andie-macdowell-bill-murray-never-going-do-groundhog-day-reboot-studio-1099307 | access-date = 2021-01-20 }}</ref>。2020年2月2日，托布罗斯基、默瑞和哥哥道尔在[[第五十四屆超級盃|第五十四屆超級盃]]的[[吉普角斗士|吉普角斗士]]广告中亮相，扮成各自在《土拨鼠之日》中的角色。广告在伍德斯托克摄制，再现片中场景，还有菲尔困在时间循环的情节，主要内容是他驾驶吉普角斗-{士}-与土拨鼠菲尔一起游览庞克瑟托尼。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Barwick | first = Ryan | title = Jeep Teases Groundhog Day-Themed Super Bowl Ad | url = https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/jeep-teases-groundhog-day-themed-super-bowl-ad/ | journal = Adweek | date = 2020-01-31 | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-11-29 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201129112133/https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/jeep-teases-groundhog-day-themed-super-bowl-ad/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Detroit Free Press | url = https://www.freep.com/story/money/cars/chrysler/2020/02/02/bill-murray-groundhog-day-super-bowl-ad/4638852002/ | title = Watch Bill Murray take a groundhog for a spin in a Jeep Gladiator | last = Lawrence | first = Eric | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125003231/https://www.freep.com/story/money/cars/chrysler/2020/02/02/bill-murray-groundhog-day-super-bowl-ad/4638852002/ | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | dead-url = no | date = 2020-02-02 | access-date = 2021-01-20 }}</ref>默瑞声称这是他演出的第一和最后一支广告<ref>{{cite news | first = Lisa | last = Respers France | title = Bill Murray's 'Groundhog Day' Super Bowl ad made us nostalgic | url = https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/03/entertainment/bill-murray-groundhog-commercial-trnd/index.html | date = 2020-02-03 | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031185413/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/02/03/entertainment/bill-murray-groundhog-commercial-trnd/index.html | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2020年4月，吉普角半士发布多种修改版广告，提倡2020年[[新冠病毒病疫情期间的社会疏离|新冠病毒病疫情期间的-{zh-cn:社会疏离;zh-tw:社交距離;}-]]，默瑞为广告修改提供创作建议<ref name="JEEPCovid" /><ref>{{cite journal | first = Dale | last = Buss | title = 'Groundhog Day'—And Bill Murray—Came Naturally To New Jeep Ads | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/dalebuss/2020/04/12/groundhog-day---and-murray---came-naturally-to-new-jeep-ads/#404e8c5e6f01 | date = 2020-04-12 | journal = Forbes | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108222653/https://www.forbes.com/sites/dalebuss/2020/04/12/groundhog-day---and-murray---came-naturally-to-new-jeep-ads/#404e8c5e6f01 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

鲁宾在电影上映后的几年里参与同名音乐剧改编，一方面找事儿干，另一方面也是因为参与音乐剧创作不违反当年和哥伦比亚影业签署的合同<ref name="telegraph interview" /><ref name="VultureRubin" />。2003年，[[史蒂芬·桑坦|史蒂芬·桑坦]]表示有意参与音乐剧创作，但始终没有落实<ref>{{cite web | first = Robert | url = https://www.playbill.com/news/article/sondheim-talks-about-bounce-revisions-in-works-114941 | title = Sondheim Talks About Bounce; Revisions in Works | journal = Playbill | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200813144147/https://www.playbill.com/news/article/sondheim-talks-about-bounce-revisions-in-works-114941 | archive-date = 2020-08-13 | dead-url = no | last = Simonson | date = 2003-08-26 }}</ref>。2012年，[[马修·沃楚斯|马修·沃楚斯]]（{{lang|en|Matthew Warchus}}）和[[蒂姆·明钦|蒂姆·明钦]]主动联系鲁宾，后者已完成叙事大纲、笑料和精心挑选的12首歌曲<ref name="telegraph interview" /><ref name="VultureRubin" />，只是没有聘请作曲家推动项目更进一步。音乐剧《[[玛蒂尔达_(音乐剧)|玛蒂尔达]]》（''{{lang|en|Matilda the Musical}}''）大获成功后，沃楚斯、明钦和鲁宾合作多年创作《土拨鼠之日》音乐剧<ref name="VultureRubin" />，2016年8月在伦敦[[舊維克劇場|舊維克劇場]]首演并获普遍好评<ref name="VultureRubin" /><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/news/kevin-spacey-s-successor-old-vic-promises-more-low-key-approach-10191051.html | title = Groundhog Day musical to premiere at Old Vic from Matilda theatre director | newspaper = The Independent | date = 2015-04-20 | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111029/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/news/kevin-spacey-s-successor-old-vic-promises-more-low-key-approach-10191051.html | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[百老匯劇院|百老汇]]版2017年开始演出<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Photo-Flash-Welcome-to-Smalltown-USA-First-Look-at-GROUNDHOG-DAY-on-Broadway-20170328 | title = Photo Flash: Welcome to Smalltown, USA! First Look at Groundhog Day on Broadway | website = BroadwayWorld | date = 2017-03-28 | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201102143129/https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Photo-Flash-Welcome-to-Smalltown-USA-First-Look-at-GROUNDHOG-DAY-on-Broadway-20170328 | archive-date = 2020-11-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。剧目获[[2017年劳伦斯·奥利弗奖|2017年]][[劳伦斯·奥利弗奖|劳伦斯·奥利弗奖]]多项提名，最后拿下最佳音乐剧男主角和最佳新音乐剧奖<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-39181027 | title = Olivier Awards 2017: Winners in full | date = 2017-04-10 | publisher = BBC News | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201102222706/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-39181027 | archive-date = 2020-11-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。鲁宾和默里兄弟曾在2017年前往观看百老汇版演出<ref>{{cite news | first = Sopan | last = Deb | title = Bill Murray Relives a Role, Seeing Broadway's 'Groundhog Day' | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/08/theater/bill-murray-groundhog-day-broadway.html | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1993-12-13 | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031910/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/08/theater/bill-murray-groundhog-day-broadway.html | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2019年9月，西班牙[[龙舌兰工作室|龙舌兰工作室]]开发的本片电子游戏续作《土拨鼠之日：有其父必有其子》（{{lang|en|''Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son''}}）问世，索尼影业虚拟现实发行，支持[[PlayStation_VR|PlayStation VR]]、[[Oculus_Rift|Oculus Rift]]和[[HTC_Vive|HTC Vive]]平方。玩家控制的小菲尔·康纳斯是片中菲尔之子，在父亲的阴影下长大。小菲尔在庞克瑟托尼陷入时间循环，必须改善自我、帮助他人才能赢得自由。<ref>{{cite web | first = Zack | last = Zweiden | url = https://kotaku.com/groundhog-day-like-father-like-son-is-a-psvr-game-and-1832290309 | title = Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son Is A PSVR Game And A Sequel To The Bill Murray Film | date = 2019-02-02 | website = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230035/https://kotaku.com/groundhog-day-like-father-like-son-is-a-psvr-game-and-1832290309 | archive-date = 2020-11-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Kyle | last = Orland | url = https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2019/02/26-years-later-groundhog-day-gets-revived-as-a-vr-game/ | title = 26 years later, Groundhog Day gets revived as… a VR game? | date = 2019-02-02 | website = [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-date = 2020-12-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201201064319/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2019/02/26-years-later-groundhog-day-gets-revived-as-a-vr-game/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | first = Hunter | last = Wolfe | url = https://www.gameinformer.com/preview/2019/02/28/new-details-on-the-odd-licensed-title | title = Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son | date = 2019-02-28 | website = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | access-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107231602/https://www.gameinformer.com/preview/2019/02/28/new-details-on-the-odd-licensed-title | archive-date = 2020-11-07 | dead-url = no | journal =  }}</ref>

